</P>
<P>
The Royal Ulster Constabulary (RUC) fired plastic bullets to
beat back the rioting mob coming from the mainly Nationalist
housing estate which was objecting to an attempt by some Loyalists
to move down the road.
</P>
<P>
A RUC spokesman said "it is the most serious rioting we have
had for a very long time and it is difficult to establish what
sparked it off."
</P>
<P>
Political observers here believe that the violence is a blow to
