<HEADLINE> Small Electric Mosquito Swatter Selling Hot </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
FUZHOU, May 31 (Xinhua) -- It may not attract one's attention
at the first sight, but the small electric mosquito swatter, a
patented product, has proved to be a hot seller on the
international market.
</P>
<P>
Developed in 1994, the swatter has become a major foreign
exchange earner for the Jiuxing (nine star) Enterprise Group.
</P>
<P>
So far, the group, located in Fuzhou, Fujian province, has
exported the swatter to over 30 countries and regions in Asia,
Europe, and Africa, earning eight million US dollars.
</P>
<P>
The invisible asset value of the mosquito swatter is assessed
by the Liancheng Asset Assessment Firm of the Patent Office of
China to be at 83 million yuan (10 million US dollars).
</P>
<P>
The Jiuxing Group has developed 86 patented products, of which
three, including the mosquito swatter, were designated as the
state key new products. Because of its achievements, the company
was selected as one of the best ten patent-application
enterprises. 
</P>
</TEXT>
